  <summary date="2023-04-14T15:19:13Z" status="Introduced in Senate">COVID-19 Vaccination Non-Discrimination Act

This bill prohibits making federal funds available to any facility that refuses to treat an individual based on the individual's COVID-19 vaccination status, including any funding under Medicare, Medicaid, or the Children's Health Insurance Program (CHIP).</summary>
